----

''FFII participated in a Brazilian event and there is now an initiative in Brazil to found a branch of FFII.''

== News ==

 * 2006-02-20 soares presents itself to the eboard. susinho answers offering help.
 * 2005-07-10 soares gets a shell account on genba
 * 2005-07-08 susinho publish a [[http://wiki.ffii.org/Fisl05En|report on FISL 6.0]]
 * 2005-07-01 soares (soares at marcusvicinius) says wants to found of FFII BR
 * 2005-06-00 susinho reports to a Brazilian event on behalf of FFII

== People ==

 * soares: [[http://marcusvinicius.eti.br/|Marcus Vinicius B. Soares]]
 * susinho: [[http://mesagalega.ffii.org/|Suso Baleato]] 

== Tasks & Progress ==

soares has taken up (some of) the following tasks.

 * document the [[SwpatbrEn| Brazilian software patent situation]]
 * conduct conferences/seminars at Brazilian events
 * promote legislation along the lines of the [[AmPlenPr050701En| 21 amendments]] or [[http://swpat.ffii.org/papers/europarl0309/amends05/juri0504/nukleus/|10 core clarifications]] 
 * register the ffii.br domain in the name of FFII.org with a local contact person, as done for ffii.gr by aptiko
 * register a local section of FFII
